               </did>
               <scopecontent id="aspace_37b2dbe0fe5061b7c4fc8944cb487188">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Southall sends Hodson a photograph of his watercolour "The Schooner" in celebration of the New Year and thanks him for offering to lend The Mirror for an exhibition although it was not used in the end.</p>
               </scopecontent>
               <controlaccess>
                  <genreform identifier="http://vocab.getty.edu/aat/300026877" source="aat">
                     <part localtype="genre_form">Correspondence </part>
                  </genreform>
               </controlaccess>
            </c>
