               </did>
               <scopecontent id="aspace_1dae4410f945b40ce5628433afd240bf">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Southall discusses frescoes and how he wished he had done more and continues on to discuss the success of the London show and its significance in exposing Birmingham work.</p>
               </scopecontent>
