                  <p>Southall tells Hodson about a one-man show he is doing in Paris and asks if Hodson would lend "Beauty at the Fountain" to be in the show.</p>
               </scopecontent>
               <controlaccess>
                  <genreform identifier="http://vocab.getty.edu/aat/300026877" source="aat">
